translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王の情報が集まらない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Can't gather any information about the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは奥の手を使う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance uses his trump card.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クレインを連れて冒険に出発
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sets out on an adventure with Crane.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クレインの特殊体質
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Crane's special constitution.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを使って魔王の情報を探す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Using that to search for information about the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅２日目
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Second day of the journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 峠の茶屋で休憩
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Resting at a teahouse on the mountain pass.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅３日目
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Third day of the journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 辺境の村で宿泊
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Staying overnight in a frontier village.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅５日目
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fifth day of the journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クレインがハニーから情報をゲット
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Crane obtains information from Honey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スルメ山に向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heading towards Mount Surume.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 霧の立ちこめるスメル山
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mount Smell shrouded in thick fog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中：リターンデーモンの呪文が発動する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: During the battle: The Return Demon spell is activated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そして飛ばされてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And they are sent flying away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２４０／戦闘／リターン発動　参照、ほぼ同じ内容
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 240 / Battle / Return Activation – Refer to this, almost the same content.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リターン、呪文が発動した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Return spell has been activated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達は飛ばされた、自由都市、どこかの平原のどまんなか、ぽつねん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and the others were teleported to the center of a plain somewhere in the Free City, all alone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、シィル、クレイン
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance, Sill, and Crane.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐはっ・・うっとおしい、元の場所に戻されてしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh... annoying, we've been sent back to the original location.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかたないですね、またスメル山に戻りましょう。魔王はそこにいます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can't be helped, let's return to Mount Smell again. The Demon Lord is there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、もういい、なんか居ない気がしてきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, that's enough. I’m starting to feel like he’s not even there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すっかりやる気のなくなったランス君
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance has completely lost his motivation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 帰る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Going home.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜クエストアウトになります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ＜You will be kicked out of the quest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 使徒ケイブワンと遭遇
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encounter with Apostle Cave One.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敗北し逃げたケイブワン
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cave One defeated and fleeing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 任務を投げだし撤収する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Abandoning the mission and retreating.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 崖から落ちでダメージ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damaged from falling off a cliff.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パステル、ベゼルアイ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pastel, Bezel Eye.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 撤収中のケイブワンがマエリータ隊と接触
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cave One makes contact with Maelita’s squad during the retreat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一緒に撤収させてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are forced to retreat together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勇者テオマンと遭遇する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encounter with the hero Teoman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 彼らも魔王を捜している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are also searching for the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人健太郎、謎の美女と遭遇
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Majin Kentarou encounters a mysterious beauty.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中の割り込みイベント　敵ＨＰ５０％以下
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Interrupt event during battle: enemy HP below 50%.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後ろから美樹が顔を出す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki peeks out from behind.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 危ない美樹ちゃんは下がっていてと健太郎は言う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kentarou says, 'Dangerous! Miki-chan, step back.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹、うん・・ごめんなさい、でも・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki: Yes... sorry, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 健太郎君がんばれー、がんばれー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go Kentarou-kun, go! Go, go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その応援を聞いて、健太郎のＨＰは全快になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hearing that encouragement, Kentarou’s HP is fully restored.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ありがとう、美樹ちゃん、百人力だよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thank you, Miki-chan. You’re worth a hundred men.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 僕は必ず君を守る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I will definitely protect you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うーん、なんかむかつく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, somehow that annoys me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっとわかるわ、それ、とかなみ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I kind of get that feeling, too — said Nanami.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹が少し離れた所で、たまに健太郎を見ています。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki stays a little distance away, occasionally glancing at Kentarou.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きちゃだめだよと言いながら、うれしい健太郎。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Telling him 'Don’t come,' Kentarou is happy nonetheless.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちらちらと後ろの美樹を見ながら戦います。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fighting while glancing at Miki behind him from time to time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 支援状態．美樹　が消された後のターン
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Support state. Turn after Miki has been erased.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後ろを見て、きょろきょろ、美樹ちゃんが居ない、どこにいった・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Looking back and around anxiously, Miki-chan is gone. Where did she go...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まさか、お前達・・美樹ちゃんに手を出したな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No way, you guys... you laid a hand on Miki-chan.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: がはははは、邪魔だから少し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahahaha, she was a nuisance, so just a little...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きさまー美樹ちゃんを殺したのかー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You bastard — did you kill Miki-chan?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、魔王殺すなんて無理だから、そんな事はしないぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, killing the Demon Lord is impossible, so we wouldn't do something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おのれー　健太郎、聞いてない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damn you — Kentarou didn’t hear any of that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王の情報が集まらない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Can't gather any information about the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは奥の手を使う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance uses his trump card.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クレインを連れて冒険に出発
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sets out on an adventure with Crane.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クレインの特殊体質
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Crane's special constitution.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを使って魔王の情報を探す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Using that to search for information about the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅２日目
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Second day of the journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 峠の茶屋で休憩
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Resting at a teahouse on the mountain pass.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅３日目
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Third day of the journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 辺境の村で宿泊
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Staying overnight in a frontier village.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅５日目
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fifth day of the journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クレインがハニーから情報をゲット
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Crane obtains information from Honey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スルメ山に向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heading towards Mount Surume.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 霧の立ちこめるスメル山
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mount Smell shrouded in thick fog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中：リターンデーモンの呪文が発動する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: During the battle: The Return Demon spell is activated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そして飛ばされてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And they are sent flying away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２４０／戦闘／リターン発動　参照、ほぼ同じ内容
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 240 / Battle / Return Activation – Refer to this, almost the same content.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リターン、呪文が発動した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Return spell has been activated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達は飛ばされた、自由都市、どこかの平原のどまんなか、ぽつねん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and the others were teleported to the center of a plain somewhere in the Free City, all alone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、シィル、クレイン
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance, Sill, and Crane.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐはっ・・うっとおしい、元の場所に戻されてしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh... annoying, we've been sent back to the original location.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかたないですね、またスメル山に戻りましょう。魔王はそこにいます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can't be helped, let's return to Mount Smell again. The Demon Lord is there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、もういい、なんか居ない気がしてきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, that's enough. I’m starting to feel like he’s not even there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すっかりやる気のなくなったランス君
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance has completely lost his motivation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 帰る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Going home.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜クエストアウトになります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ＜You will be kicked out of the quest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 使徒ケイブワンと遭遇
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encounter with Apostle Cave One.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敗北し逃げたケイブワン
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cave One defeated and fleeing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 任務を投げだし撤収する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Abandoning the mission and retreating.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 崖から落ちでダメージ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damaged from falling off a cliff.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パステル、ベゼルアイ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pastel, Bezel Eye.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 撤収中のケイブワンがマエリータ隊と接触
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cave One makes contact with Maelita’s squad during the retreat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一緒に撤収させてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are forced to retreat together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勇者テオマンと遭遇する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Encounter with the hero Teoman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 彼らも魔王を捜している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are also searching for the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人健太郎、謎の美女と遭遇
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Majin Kentarou encounters a mysterious beauty.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中の割り込みイベント　敵ＨＰ５０％以下
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Interrupt event during battle: enemy HP below 50%.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後ろから美樹が顔を出す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki peeks out from behind.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 危ない美樹ちゃんは下がっていてと健太郎は言う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kentarou says, 'Dangerous! Miki-chan, step back.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹、うん・・ごめんなさい、でも・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki: Yes... sorry, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 健太郎君がんばれー、がんばれー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go Kentarou-kun, go! Go, go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その応援を聞いて、健太郎のＨＰは全快になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hearing that encouragement, Kentarou’s HP is fully restored.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ありがとう、美樹ちゃん、百人力だよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thank you, Miki-chan. You’re worth a hundred men.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 僕は必ず君を守る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I will definitely protect you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うーん、なんかむかつく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, somehow that annoys me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっとわかるわ、それ、とかなみ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I kind of get that feeling, too — said Nanami.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹が少し離れた所で、たまに健太郎を見ています。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki stays a little distance away, occasionally glancing at Kentarou.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きちゃだめだよと言いながら、うれしい健太郎。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Telling him 'Don’t come,' Kentarou is happy nonetheless.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちらちらと後ろの美樹を見ながら戦います。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fighting while glancing at Miki behind him from time to time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 支援状態．美樹　が消された後のターン
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Support state. Turn after Miki has been erased.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後ろを見て、きょろきょろ、美樹ちゃんが居ない、どこにいった・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Looking back and around anxiously, Miki-chan is gone. Where did she go...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まさか、お前達・・美樹ちゃんに手を出したな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No way, you guys... you laid a hand on Miki-chan.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: がはははは、邪魔だから少し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahahaha, she was a nuisance, so just a little...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きさまー美樹ちゃんを殺したのかー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You bastard — did you kill Miki-chan?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、魔王殺すなんて無理だから、そんな事はしないぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, killing the Demon Lord is impossible, so we wouldn't do something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おのれー　健太郎、聞いてない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damn you — Kentarou didn’t hear any of that.
